<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_242_r2l17">Burgraf cʒu Miltemberg / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_242_r2l18">Lıeber etc . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger vnd kauflewt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r2l19">ın die <expan>nechſtk<ex>ünftige</ex></expan> herbſtmeſſe / gen frankfurtt / vnd <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darauſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r2l20">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvenn </del> mit ſıcherm geleite gunſtıklıchen fürſehen wollet / <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r2l21"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> geleite vnd gepiet geet / etc . ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> . / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_242" id="119v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burgraf czu Miltemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber etc. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger und kauflewt in die
                                <expan>nechstk<ex>ünftige</ex></expan> herbstmesse gen Frankfurtt
                        und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darausz mit sicherm geleite gunstiklichen
                        fürsehen wollet, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> geleite und gepiet geet etc. ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
